<br>
The forums are either open to everyone to &quot;view&quot; or password protected.<br>
<br>
The guilds involved have requested it be a private forum.  One that will be opened to guilds as they achieve Ele Plane Access.  The &quot;etiquette&quot;, once decided, will be added into the appropriate section.<br>
<br>
